"-------------------- VISUAL SETTINGS

"background of line numbers the same as the vim window
hi LineNr ctermbg=bg

"background of split line for splits is the same as the vim window
hi vertsplit ctermbg=bg ctermfg=bg

"background of whitespace highlighting
hi ExtraWhitespace ctermbg=white

"highlight bad spelling
hi SpellBad ctermbg=black ctermfg=white

"background of sign gutter (ALE) same as vim window
hi SignColumn ctermbg=bg
